<div class="post-entry-content">
<h3 class="ele-entry-title"><a href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/news-zh/19828/" rel="bookmark" title="2026-2027 中一入學資訊日">2026-2027 中一入學資訊日</a></h3><div class="entry-meta"><a href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/date/2025/11/26/" title="9:25 上午" class="meta-item data-link" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date updated" datetime="2025-11-26T09:25:28+08:00">26/11/2025</time></a></div><div class="entry-excerpt"><p>本校將於 2025 年 11 月 29 日（星期六）舉辦 2026-2027 中一入學資訊日，當日除了羅楚雲校長主持入學講座外，更會有學科嘉年華、課外活動體驗、學生表演及校園參觀等等，歡迎家長和學生參加。如有興趣了解更多本校的校園設施、學術課程、全人發展活動、價值觀教育和其他學科課程，請填寫網上報名表格。 報名表格 交通資訊</p>
</div><a href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/news-zh/19828/" target="" aria-label="Read more about 2026-2027 中一入學資訊日" class="box-button elementor-button elementor-size-xs">更多<svg aria-hidden="true" class="elementor-button-icon e-font-icon-svg e-fas-arrow-right" viewBox="0 0 448 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M190.5 66.9l22.2-22.2c9.4-9.4 24.6-9.4 33.9 0L441 239c9.4 9.4 9.4 24.6 0 33.9L246.6 467.3c-9.4 9.4-24.6 9.4-33.9 0l-22.2-22.2c-9.5-9.5-9.3-25 .4-34.3L311.4 296H24c-13.3 0-24-10.7-24-24v-32c0-13.3 10.7-24 24-24h287.4L190.9 101.2c-9.8-9.3-10-24.8-.4-34.3z"></path></svg></a>
</div></article><article class="post visible post-29746 type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-news-zh">
<div class="post-thumbnail-wrap">
<div class="post-thumbnail">
<a class="post-thumbnail-rollover layzr-bg img-css-resize-wrapper" aria-label="Post image" href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/news-zh/29746/"><img decoding="async" width="1132" height="442" src="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/26092305/%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3%E6%B5%B7%E5%A0%B1%EF%BC%88QR-code11.jpeg" class="attachment-full size-full preload-me aspect lazy lazy-load" alt="" sizes="(max-width: 1132px) 100vw, 1132px" style="--ratio: 1132 / 442;" data-src="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/26092305/%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3%E6%B5%B7%E5%A0%B1%EF%BC%88QR-code11.jpeg" loading="eager" data-srcset="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/26092305/%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3%E6%B5%B7%E5%A0%B1%EF%BC%88QR-code11.jpeg 1132w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/26092305/%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3%E6%B5%B7%E5%A0%B1%EF%BC%88QR-code11-300x117.jpeg 300w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/26092305/%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3%E6%B5%B7%E5%A0%B1%EF%BC%88QR-code11-1024x400.jpeg 1024w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/26092305/%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3%E6%B5%B7%E5%A0%B1%EF%BC%88QR-code11-768x300.jpeg 768w" /></a>
