<div class="post-entry-content">
<h3 class="ele-entry-title"><a href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/news-zh/29746/" rel="bookmark" title="香港真光書院: 小學數學邀請賽2025">香港真光書院: 小學數學邀請賽2025</a></h3><div class="entry-meta"><a href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/date/2025/11/21/" title="9:23 上午" class="meta-item data-link" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date updated" datetime="2025-11-21T09:23:04+08:00">21/11/2025</time></a></div><div class="entry-excerpt"><p>本校一向秉承基督博愛與犧牲的精神，致力推廣女子全人教育，重視德、智、體、群、美、靈六育均衡發展，並培養學生創新、服務、克己和追求卓越的真光精神。 本校將於2025年12月20日（星期六）上午，假香港真光書院舉辦《小學數學邀請賽2025》。比賽內容涵蓋小一至小六數學課程及部分課外知識，旨在提升學生的數學能力及邏輯思維。比賽設有個人及團體獎項。 現誠邀 各校表現優異的女學生參賽。凡於賽事中獲得優異成績&#8230;</p>
</div><a href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/news-zh/29746/" target="" aria-label="Read more about 香港真光書院: 小學數學邀請賽2025" class="box-button elementor-button elementor-size-xs">更多<svg aria-hidden="true" class="elementor-button-icon e-font-icon-svg e-fas-arrow-right" viewBox="0 0 448 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M190.5 66.9l22.2-22.2c9.4-9.4 24.6-9.4 33.9 0L441 239c9.4 9.4 9.4 24.6 0 33.9L246.6 467.3c-9.4 9.4-24.6 9.4-33.9 0l-22.2-22.2c-9.5-9.5-9.3-25 .4-34.3L311.4 296H24c-13.3 0-24-10.7-24-24v-32c0-13.3 10.7-24 24-24h287.4L190.9 101.2c-9.8-9.3-10-24.8-.4-34.3z"></path></svg></a>
</div></article><article class="post visible post-29449 type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-news-zh category-events-zh tag-science-zh tag-technology-zh">
<div class="post-thumbnail-wrap">
<div class="post-thumbnail">
<a class="post-thumbnail-rollover layzr-bg img-css-resize-wrapper" aria-label="Post image" href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/events-zh/29449/"><img decoding="async" width="1600" height="1200" src="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/12101929/Copy-of-6a31d47a-a7e8-4795-8504-dcd84fc1f408.jpeg" class="attachment-full size-full preload-me aspect lazy lazy-load" alt="" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" style="--ratio: 1600 / 1200;" data-src="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/12101929/Copy-of-6a31d47a-a7e8-4795-8504-dcd84fc1f408.jpeg" loading="eager" data-srcset="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/12101929/Copy-of-6a31d47a-a7e8-4795-8504-dcd84fc1f408.jpeg 1600w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/12101929/Copy-of-6a31d47a-a7e8-4795-8504-dcd84fc1f408-300x225.jpeg 300w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/12101929/Copy-of-6a31d47a-a7e8-4795-8504-dcd84fc1f408-1024x768.jpeg 1024w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/12101929/Copy-of-6a31d47a-a7e8-4795-8504-dcd84fc1f408-768x576.jpeg 768w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/12101929/Copy-of-6a31d47a-a7e8-4795-8504-dcd84fc1f408-1536x1152.jpeg 1536w" /></a>
