<div class="post-thumbnail">
<a class="post-thumbnail-rollover layzr-bg img-css-resize-wrapper" aria-label="Post image" href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/achievements-zh/30532/"><img decoding="async" width="1600" height="1200" src="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/11113744/%E9%84%BA%E5%BE%B7%E5%A7%B85B08_2025%E7%AC%AC%E5%85%AB%E5%B1%86-%E5%85%A8%E6%B8%AF%E9%9D%92%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E9%80%B2%E6%AD%A5%E7%8D%8E1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full preload-me aspect lazy lazy-load" alt="" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" style="--ratio: 1600 / 1200;" data-src="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/11113744/%E9%84%BA%E5%BE%B7%E5%A7%B85B08_2025%E7%AC%AC%E5%85%AB%E5%B1%86-%E5%85%A8%E6%B8%AF%E9%9D%92%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E9%80%B2%E6%AD%A5%E7%8D%8E1.jpg" loading="eager" data-srcset="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/11113744/%E9%84%BA%E5%BE%B7%E5%A7%B85B08_2025%E7%AC%AC%E5%85%AB%E5%B1%86-%E5%85%A8%E6%B8%AF%E9%9D%92%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E9%80%B2%E6%AD%A5%E7%8D%8E1.jpg 1600w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/11113744/%E9%84%BA%E5%BE%B7%E5%A7%B85B08_2025%E7%AC%AC%E5%85%AB%E5%B1%86-%E5%85%A8%E6%B8%AF%E9%9D%92%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E9%80%B2%E6%AD%A5%E7%8D%8E1-300x225.jpg 300w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/11113744/%E9%84%BA%E5%BE%B7%E5%A7%B85B08_2025%E7%AC%AC%E5%85%AB%E5%B1%86-%E5%85%A8%E6%B8%AF%E9%9D%92%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E9%80%B2%E6%AD%A5%E7%8D%8E1-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/11113744/%E9%84%BA%E5%BE%B7%E5%A7%B85B08_2025%E7%AC%AC%E5%85%AB%E5%B1%86-%E5%85%A8%E6%B8%AF%E9%9D%92%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E9%80%B2%E6%AD%A5%E7%8D%8E1-768x576.jpg 768w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/11113744/%E9%84%BA%E5%BE%B7%E5%A7%B85B08_2025%E7%AC%AC%E5%85%AB%E5%B1%86-%E5%85%A8%E6%B8%AF%E9%9D%92%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E9%80%B2%E6%AD%A5%E7%8D%8E1-1536x1152.jpg 1536w" /></a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="post-entry-content">
<h4 class="ele-entry-title"><a href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/achievements-zh/30532/" rel="bookmark" title="2025第八屆全港青少年進步獎">2025第八屆全港青少年進步獎</a></h4><div class="entry-excerpt"><p>本校中五級鄺德姸同學於「2025第八屆全港青少年進步獎」，榮獲「全港青少年進步獎」。 鄺同學於2026年1月30日出席頒獎典禮，並獲頒發獎狀乙張及獎學金港幣500元正。 獲獎同學感受： 能夠出席由杜葉錫恩教育基金舉辦之全港青少年進步獎頒獎典禮，實在是一段難得且極具意義的經歷。典禮上，各得獎同學均展現堅毅不懈之精神，令我深切體會到「進步」並非僅指學業成績之提升，而是涵蓋自我突破與持續努力的態度。教育&#8230;</p>
</div>
</div></article><article class="post visible post-30412 type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-achievements-zh category-events-zh tag-science-zh">
<div class="post-thumbnail-wrap">
<div class="post-thumbnail">
<a class="post-thumbnail-rollover layzr-bg img-css-resize-wrapper" aria-label="Post image" href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/achievements-zh/30412/"><img decoding="async" width="1600" height="900" src="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/28120230/9de34dfe-94af-4929-9aa1-93e189050adc.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full preload-me aspect lazy lazy-load" alt="" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" style="--ratio: 1600 / 900;" data-src="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/28120230/9de34dfe-94af-4929-9aa1-93e189050adc.jpg" loading="eager" data-srcset="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/28120230/9de34dfe-94af-4929-9aa1-93e189050adc.jpg 1600w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/28120230/9de34dfe-94af-4929-9aa1-93e189050adc-300x169.jpg 300w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/28120230/9de34dfe-94af-4929-9aa1-93e189050adc-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/28120230/9de34dfe-94af-4929-9aa1-93e189050adc-768x432.jpg 768w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/28120230/9de34dfe-94af-4929-9aa1-93e189050adc-1536x864.jpg 1536w" /></a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="post-entry-content">
<h4 class="ele-entry-title"><a href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/achievements-zh/30412/" rel="bookmark" title="《第一屆全港生命教育巡禮》暨《中華瀕危物種保育計劃嘉許禮》">《第一屆全港生命教育巡禮》暨《中華瀕危物種保育計劃嘉許禮》</a></h4><div class="entry-excerpt"><p>隨著教育使命的推進，本校持續致力於培養學生的保育意識及對生態的關注。本校「動物護理及生物科研學會」於2026年1月24至25日帶領學生到慕光英文書院參加《第一屆全港生命教育巡禮》暨《中華瀕危物種保育計劃嘉許禮》，並榮獲中華瀕危物種保育計劃感謝狀及熱心推廣兩棲及爬行教育嘉許狀。 此獎項旨在表揚本校在推廣兩棲及爬行類動物教育的卓越貢獻，特別是對於校內建立「爬蟲生態閣」的努力予以肯定。這不僅為學生提供了&#8230;</p>
</div>
</div></article><article class="post visible post-30541 type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-achievements-zh tag-career-zh">
<div class="post-thumbnail-wrap">
<div class="post-thumbnail">
<a class="post-thumbnail-rollover layzr-bg img-css-resize-wrapper" aria-label="Post image" href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/achievements-zh/30541/"><img decoding="async" width="2560" height="1610" src="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/11114016/%E9%A0%98%E5%B1%95%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%8D%8E%E5%AD%B8%E9%87%912025-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full preload-me aspect lazy lazy-load" alt="" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" style="--ratio: 2560 / 1610;" data-src="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/11114016/%E9%A0%98%E5%B1%95%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%8D%8E%E5%AD%B8%E9%87%912025-scaled.jpg" loading="eager" data-srcset="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/11114016/%E9%A0%98%E5%B1%95%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%8D%8E%E5%AD%B8%E9%87%912025-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/11114016/%E9%A0%98%E5%B1%95%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%8D%8E%E5%AD%B8%E9%87%912025-300x189.jpg 300w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/11114016/%E9%A0%98%E5%B1%95%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%8D%8E%E5%AD%B8%E9%87%912025-1024x644.jpg 1024w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/11114016/%E9%A0%98%E5%B1%95%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%8D%8E%E5%AD%B8%E9%87%912025-768x483.jpg 768w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/11114016/%E9%A0%98%E5%B1%95%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%8D%8E%E5%AD%B8%E9%87%912025-1536x966.jpg 1536w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/11114016/%E9%A0%98%E5%B1%95%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%8D%8E%E5%AD%B8%E9%87%912025-2048x1288.jpg 2048w" /></a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="post-entry-content">
<h4 class="ele-entry-title"><a href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/achievements-zh/30541/" rel="bookmark" title="領展大學生獎學金2025">領展大學生獎學金2025</a></h4><div class="entry-excerpt"><p>本校畢業生梁綽敏同學榮獲領展大學生獎學金 &#8211; 大學一年級獎學金。獎學金資助家庭三代中第一代入讀本地大學的學生。除了獎學金外，更成立領展同學會，舉辦不同社區參與活動，讓得獎學生拓寬視野，協助他們實踐理想及增加向上流動的機會。 梁同學於2026年1月24日出席頒獎典禮，並獲頒發獎狀乙張及獎學金港幣20000元正。</p>
</div>
</div></article><article class="post visible post-30222 type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-achievements-zh tag-physical-education-zh">
<div class="post-thumbnail-wrap">
<div class="post-thumbnail">
<a class="post-thumbnail-rollover layzr-bg img-css-resize-wrapper" aria-label="Post image" href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/achievements-zh/30222/"><img decoding="async" width="1600" height="1200" src="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/14085818/WhatsApp-Image-2026-01-04-at-5.29.50-PM.jpeg" class="attachment-full size-full preload-me aspect lazy lazy-load" alt="" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" style="--ratio: 1600 / 1200;" data-src="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/14085818/WhatsApp-Image-2026-01-04-at-5.29.50-PM.jpeg" loading="eager" data-srcset="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/14085818/WhatsApp-Image-2026-01-04-at-5.29.50-PM.jpeg 1600w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/14085818/WhatsApp-Image-2026-01-04-at-5.29.50-PM-300x225.jpeg 300w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/14085818/WhatsApp-Image-2026-01-04-at-5.29.50-PM-1024x768.jpeg 1024w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/14085818/WhatsApp-Image-2026-01-04-at-5.29.50-PM-768x576.jpeg 768w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/14085818/WhatsApp-Image-2026-01-04-at-5.29.50-PM-1536x1152.jpeg 1536w" /></a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="post-entry-content">
<h4 class="ele-entry-title"><a href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/achievements-zh/30222/" rel="bookmark" title="2026 隊際外展劍擊(花劍)">2026 隊際外展劍擊(花劍)</a></h4><div class="entry-excerpt"><p>本校中六葉曦彤、中五劉詩穎、中四梁翯焉及中三蘇嘉寶同學於2026年1月4日參加外展劍擊比賽（花劍），經過一整天激烈的賽事，最終勇奪冠軍。恭喜各位同學為校爭光，展現出堅毅不屈和團隊合作的精神。</p>
</div>
</div></article><article class="post visible post-30360 type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-achievements-zh category-events-zh tag-student-work-zh">
<div class="post-thumbnail-wrap">
<div class="post-thumbnail">
<a class="post-thumbnail-rollover layzr-bg img-css-resize-wrapper" aria-label="Post image" href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/achievements-zh/30360/"><img decoding="async" width="2560" height="1920" src="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/20160402/IMG_7481-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full preload-me aspect lazy lazy-load" alt="" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" style="--ratio: 2560 / 1920;" data-src="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/20160402/IMG_7481-scaled.jpg" loading="eager" data-srcset="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/20160402/IMG_7481-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/20160402/IMG_7481-300x225.jpg 300w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/20160402/IMG_7481-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/20160402/IMG_7481-768x576.jpg 768w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/20160402/IMG_7481-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/20160402/IMG_7481-2048x1536.jpg 2048w" /></a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="post-entry-content">
<h4 class="ele-entry-title"><a href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/achievements-zh/30360/" rel="bookmark" title="「你眼中的物流」IG Reels拍攝比賽頒獎典禮">「你眼中的物流」IG Reels拍攝比賽頒獎典禮</a></h4><div class="entry-excerpt"><p>為配合本年度學校發展計劃「積極求知」，升學及就業輔導委員會為學生報名參加由香港物流協會主辦、教育局支持的「你眼中的物流」全港中學生IG Reels拍攝比賽。透過實地考察及製作創意影片，除了讓師生更了解香港物流業的運作和發展，亦可擴闊學生未來升學就業的路向。 本校中五許婷婷、林婉淇、何思婷及劉浠彤於2025年12月12日出席頒獎典禮，最終榮獲IG Reels「最受歡迎獎」及「最高觀看率獎」，並獲頒獎&#8230;</p>
</div>
</div></article><article class="post visible post-30370 type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-achievements-zh tag-physical-education-zh">
<div class="post-thumbnail-wrap">
<div class="post-thumbnail">
<a class="post-thumbnail-rollover layzr-bg img-css-resize-wrapper" aria-label="Post image" href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/achievements-zh/30370/"><img decoding="async" width="2560" height="1920" src="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/20160727/%E6%B8%AF%E5%B3%B6%E7%B8%BD%E5%8D%80%E7%A6%81%E6%AF%92%E5%85%B1%E8%9E%8D%E6%8E%92%E7%90%83%E8%B3%BD02-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full preload-me aspect lazy lazy-load" alt="" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" style="--ratio: 2560 / 1920;" data-src="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/20160727/%E6%B8%AF%E5%B3%B6%E7%B8%BD%E5%8D%80%E7%A6%81%E6%AF%92%E5%85%B1%E8%9E%8D%E6%8E%92%E7%90%83%E8%B3%BD02-scaled.jpg" loading="eager" data-srcset="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/20160727/%E6%B8%AF%E5%B3%B6%E7%B8%BD%E5%8D%80%E7%A6%81%E6%AF%92%E5%85%B1%E8%9E%8D%E6%8E%92%E7%90%83%E8%B3%BD02-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/20160727/%E6%B8%AF%E5%B3%B6%E7%B8%BD%E5%8D%80%E7%A6%81%E6%AF%92%E5%85%B1%E8%9E%8D%E6%8E%92%E7%90%83%E8%B3%BD02-300x225.jpg 300w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/20160727/%E6%B8%AF%E5%B3%B6%E7%B8%BD%E5%8D%80%E7%A6%81%E6%AF%92%E5%85%B1%E8%9E%8D%E6%8E%92%E7%90%83%E8%B3%BD02-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/20160727/%E6%B8%AF%E5%B3%B6%E7%B8%BD%E5%8D%80%E7%A6%81%E6%AF%92%E5%85%B1%E8%9E%8D%E6%8E%92%E7%90%83%E8%B3%BD02-768x576.jpg 768w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/20160727/%E6%B8%AF%E5%B3%B6%E7%B8%BD%E5%8D%80%E7%A6%81%E6%AF%92%E5%85%B1%E8%9E%8D%E6%8E%92%E7%90%83%E8%B3%BD02-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/20160727/%E6%B8%AF%E5%B3%B6%E7%B8%BD%E5%8D%80%E7%A6%81%E6%AF%92%E5%85%B1%E8%9E%8D%E6%8E%92%E7%90%83%E8%B3%BD02-2048x1536.jpg 2048w" /></a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="post-entry-content">
<h4 class="ele-entry-title"><a href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/achievements-zh/30370/" rel="bookmark" title="西區警區‧「港島總區禁毒共融排球賽」">西區警區‧「港島總區禁毒共融排球賽」</a></h4><div class="entry-excerpt"><p>本校排球隊於2025年11月12日參加由西區警區主辦「港島總區禁毒共融排球賽」，獲得季軍。是次比賽透過有益身心的排球比賽，建立健康生活模式，藉此提醒年輕人時刻謹記「遠離毒品」。 參賽學生：中一鄭芯嵐中二梁藤熹中二芮藴芝中三盧祉晴中三陳鋇璇中三麥楚兒中四郭蘊姿中四張玟琋中五楊珮孜</p>
</div>
</div></article><article class="post visible post-29779 type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-achievements-zh tag-personal-social-humanities-zh tag-student-work-zh">
<div class="post-thumbnail-wrap">
<div class="post-thumbnail">
<a class="post-thumbnail-rollover layzr-bg img-css-resize-wrapper" aria-label="Post image" href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/achievements-zh/29779/"><img decoding="async" width="2560" height="1920" src="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/28101445/IMG_0740-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full preload-me aspect lazy lazy-load" alt="" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" style="--ratio: 2560 / 1920;" data-src="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/28101445/IMG_0740-scaled.jpg" loading="eager" data-srcset="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/28101445/IMG_0740-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/28101445/IMG_0740-300x225.jpg 300w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/28101445/IMG_0740-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/28101445/IMG_0740-768x576.jpg 768w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/28101445/IMG_0740-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/28101445/IMG_0740-2048x1536.jpg 2048w" /></a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="post-entry-content">
<h4 class="ele-entry-title"><a href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/achievements-zh/29779/" rel="bookmark" title="「畫說抗戰」—— 全港高中學生抗戰遺址資訊圖表創作比賽">「畫說抗戰」—— 全港高中學生抗戰遺址資訊圖表創作比賽</a></h4><div class="entry-excerpt"><p>中國歷史科參與了由教育局主辦，中國文化研究院協辦的「畫說抗戰」—— 全港中學生創作比賽。5C王儷凝同學榮獲全港冠軍及最具創意獎兩大獎項，5E許蔚欣同學榮獲優異獎。王儷凝同學除了在頒獎禮中分享創作意念和歷程外，並於典禮後進行訪問拍攝。</p>
</div>
</div></article><article class="post visible post-29783 type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-achievements-zh tag-personal-social-humanities-zh">
<div class="post-thumbnail-wrap">
<div class="post-thumbnail">
<a class="post-thumbnail-rollover layzr-bg img-css-resize-wrapper" aria-label="Post image" href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/achievements-zh/29783/"><img decoding="async" width="1600" height="1200" src="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/14085130/408D0B01-6EA1-4536-B094-8718B76DE8B9.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full preload-me aspect lazy lazy-load" alt="" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" style="--ratio: 1600 / 1200;" data-src="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/14085130/408D0B01-6EA1-4536-B094-8718B76DE8B9.jpg" loading="eager" data-srcset="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/14085130/408D0B01-6EA1-4536-B094-8718B76DE8B9.jpg 1600w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/14085130/408D0B01-6EA1-4536-B094-8718B76DE8B9-300x225.jpg 300w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/14085130/408D0B01-6EA1-4536-B094-8718B76DE8B9-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/14085130/408D0B01-6EA1-4536-B094-8718B76DE8B9-768x576.jpg 768w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/14085130/408D0B01-6EA1-4536-B094-8718B76DE8B9-1536x1152.jpg 1536w" /></a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="post-entry-content">
<h4 class="ele-entry-title"><a href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/achievements-zh/29783/" rel="bookmark" title="《基本法》「傳承」跑 ── 全港青年城市定向大獎賽">《基本法》「傳承」跑 ── 全港青年城市定向大獎賽</a></h4><div class="entry-excerpt"><p>《基本法》「傳承」跑 ── 全港青年城市定向大獎賽 為加深同學了解香港的歷史和文化，明白《憲法》、《基本法》與生活息息相關，建立積極健康的人生價值觀。</p>
</div>
</div></article><article class="post visible post-30288 type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-achievements-zh tag-personal-social-humanities-zh">
<div class="post-thumbnail-wrap">
<div class="post-thumbnail">
<a class="post-thumbnail-rollover layzr-bg img-css-resize-wrapper" aria-label="Post image" href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/achievements-zh/30288/"><img decoding="async" width="2560" height="1920" src="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/14091627/IMG_0712-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full preload-me aspect lazy lazy-load" alt="" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" style="--ratio: 2560 / 1920;" data-src="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/14091627/IMG_0712-scaled.jpg" loading="eager" data-srcset="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/14091627/IMG_0712-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/14091627/IMG_0712-300x225.jpg 300w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/14091627/IMG_0712-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/14091627/IMG_0712-768x576.jpg 768w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/14091627/IMG_0712-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/14091627/IMG_0712-2048x1536.jpg 2048w" /></a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="post-entry-content">
<h4 class="ele-entry-title"><a href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/achievements-zh/30288/" rel="bookmark" title="「憲法和《基本法》演講比賽 2025 」總決賽">「憲法和《基本法》演講比賽 2025 」總決賽</a></h4><div class="entry-excerpt"><p>本校中華文化及國民教育組邀請了5位學生參加「憲法和《基本法》演講比賽2025」。其中，中六周曼喬同學及中四田梓瀅同學入圍全港二十強，並於2025年11月15日下午與其他學校如皇仁書院 、浸信會呂明才中學、協恩中學、香港培道中學及旅港開平商會中學等競逐獎項。比賽設有冠、亞、季、殿、優異獎及優良獎，競爭非常激烈，兩位學生表現仍然非常優秀，憑藉穩定的發揮，田同學和周同學分別獲得季軍及優異獎，為校爭光。</p>
</div>
</div></article><article class="post visible post-29102 type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-achievements-zh tag-chinese-zh">
<div class="post-thumbnail-wrap">
<div class="post-thumbnail">
<a class="post-thumbnail-rollover layzr-bg img-css-resize-wrapper" aria-label="Post image" href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/achievements-zh/29102/"><img decoding="async" width="2560" height="1920" src="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/10101340/IMG_5291-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full preload-me aspect lazy lazy-load" alt="" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" style="--ratio: 2560 / 1920;" data-src="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/10101340/IMG_5291-scaled.jpg" loading="eager" data-srcset="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/10101340/IMG_5291-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/10101340/IMG_5291-300x225.jpg 300w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/10101340/IMG_5291-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/10101340/IMG_5291-768x576.jpg 768w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/10101340/IMG_5291-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/10101340/IMG_5291-2048x1536.jpg 2048w" /></a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="post-entry-content">
<h4 class="ele-entry-title"><a href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/achievements-zh/29102/" rel="bookmark" title="「我愛我的祖國‧抗戰勝利篇」金紫荊盃香港校際作文暨普通話朗誦大賽">「我愛我的祖國‧抗戰勝利篇」金紫荊盃香港校際作文暨普通話朗誦大賽</a></h4><div class="entry-excerpt"><p>為提升學生的作文及朗誦水平，本校普通話科鼓勵同學參加由教育局支持的「我愛我的祖國‧抗戰勝利篇」金紫荊盃香港校際作文暨普通話朗誦大賽。 本校中五級許婷婷及王采彥同學成功擠身於2025年9月21日舉行的複賽，更榮獲二等獎，獲學校獎盃一座、學生獎狀及港幣800元獎金，並於2025年10月5日出席頒獎典禮。</p>
</div>
</div></article><article class="post visible post-29173 type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-achievements-zh tag-personal-social-humanities-zh tag-social-services-zh">
<div class="post-thumbnail-wrap">
<div class="post-thumbnail">
<a class="post-thumbnail-rollover layzr-bg img-css-resize-wrapper" aria-label="Post image" href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/achievements-zh/29173/"><img decoding="async" width="7728" height="5054" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D&#039;http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg&#039;%20viewBox%3D&#039;0%200%207728%205054&#039;%2F%3E" class="attachment-full size-full preload-me aspect lazy lazy-load" alt="" sizes="(max-width: 7728px) 100vw, 7728px" style="--ratio: 7728 / 5054;" data-src="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/20251004_event_0224.jpg" loading="eager" data-srcset="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/20251004_event_0224.jpg 7728w, https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/20251004_event_0224-300x196.jpg 300w, https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/20251004_event_0224-1024x670.jpg 1024w, https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/20251004_event_0224-768x502.jpg 768w, https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/20251004_event_0224-1536x1005.jpg 1536w" /></a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="post-entry-content">
<h4 class="ele-entry-title"><a href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/achievements-zh/29173/" rel="bookmark" title="「感創敢為 3.0 — 青年社會創新服務獎」 2024-2025">「感創敢為 3.0 — 青年社會創新服務獎」 2024-2025</a></h4><div class="entry-excerpt"><p>為鼓勵學生由同理心出發，深入了解社會問題，為社會帶來解決問題的嶄新思維，促進社會效益，本校中四至中六級健社科學生共組成9隊參賽隊伍，參加香港小童群益會舉辧的「感創敢為 3.0 — 青年社會創新服務獎」2024-2025 比賽，研發創新點子。有關隊伍已於暑假期間進行社區服務研習，深化點子方案。其中三支隊伍「光之守護者」、「狂熱真光」及「耆趣兵團」榮獲優異獎，而隊伍「真光小星星」以「耆老動感趣味」點子&#8230;</p>
</div>
</div></article><article class="post visible post-29263 type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-achievements-zh tag-physical-education-zh">
<div class="post-thumbnail-wrap">
<div class="post-thumbnail">
<a class="post-thumbnail-rollover layzr-bg img-css-resize-wrapper" aria-label="Post image" href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/achievements-zh/29263/"><img decoding="async" width="1497" height="820" src="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/28103835/WhatsApp-Image-2025-10-02-at-6.41.32-PM.jpeg" class="attachment-full size-full preload-me aspect lazy lazy-load" alt="" sizes="(max-width: 1497px) 100vw, 1497px" style="--ratio: 1497 / 820;" data-src="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/28103835/WhatsApp-Image-2025-10-02-at-6.41.32-PM.jpeg" loading="eager" data-srcset="https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/28103835/WhatsApp-Image-2025-10-02-at-6.41.32-PM.jpeg 1497w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/28103835/WhatsApp-Image-2025-10-02-at-6.41.32-PM-300x164.jpeg 300w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/28103835/WhatsApp-Image-2025-10-02-at-6.41.32-PM-1024x561.jpeg 1024w, https://media.hktlc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/28103835/WhatsApp-Image-2025-10-02-at-6.41.32-PM-768x421.jpeg 768w" /></a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="post-entry-content">
<h4 class="ele-entry-title"><a href="https://www.hktlc.edu.hk/achievements-zh/29263/" rel="bookmark" title="學界游泳比賽">學界游泳比賽</a></h4><div class="entry-excerpt"><p>本校游泳隊於十月的學界游泳比賽表現良好，同學經過艱辛的訓練，提升技巧，最後取得優異成績。甲組 5A 梁沛融獲50米蛙殿軍及100米蛙泳殿軍。丙組 2C陳彥葶獲50米蛙季軍及100米蛙泳季軍。</p>
</div>
</div></article></div><div class="owl-nav disabled"><div class="owl-prev" role="button"><svg class="e-font-icon-svg e-fas-chevron-left" viewBox="0 0 320 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M34.52 239.03L228.87 44.69c9.37-9.37 24.57-9.37 33.94 0l22.67 22.67c9.36 9.36 9.37 24.52.04 33.9L131.49 256l154.02 154.75c9.34 9.38 9.32 24.54-.04 33.9l-22.67 22.67c-9.37 9.37-24.57 9.37-33.94 0L34.52 272.97c-9.37-9.37-9.37-24.57 0-33.94z"></path></svg></div><div class="owl-next" role="button"><svg class="e-font-icon-svg e-fas-chevron-right" viewBox="0 0 320 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M285.476 272.971L91.132 467.314c-9.373 9.373-24.569 9.373-33.941 0l-22.667-22.667c-9.357-9.357-9.375-24.522-.04-33.901L188.505 256 34.484 101.255c-9.335-9.379-9.317-24.544.04-33.901l22.667-22.667c9.373-9.373 24.569-9.373 33.941 0L285.475 239.03c9.373 9.372 9.373 24.568.001 33.941z"></path></svg></div></div>				</div>
